{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"19485-boro-na-skarfaloso","title":"Μπορώ να σκαρφαλώσω!","description":"Ένα μικρό αγόρι μαθαίνει να σκαρφαλώνει. Μπορε΄ι όμως να κατέβει κάτω; Αυτό το βιβλίο είναι ένα απο τα τέσσερα βιβλία στην σειρά 'Μεγαλώνω'.","language":"Greek","langCode":"el","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Stella Stylianidou"],"illustrators":["Deval Maniar"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/19485-boro-na-skarfaloso"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/705479/size3/57c8c82ddc4444a38929edee69280586.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/705479/size6/57c8c82ddc4444a38929edee69280586.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10296/size6/181ab632f1a87a35d9047592ee73c38c.jpg","text":"Είμαι μεγάλο αγόρι τώρα.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10297/size6/4d49fae924a80cb1af9ba6f2e58033ee.jpg","text":"Μπορώ να ανεβώ τα σκαλιά.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10299/size6/37cc47b386e17285c685aa226d0d09f8.jpg","text":"Αλλά δεν μπορώ να κατέβω κάτω πάλι.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10300/size6/a6ed8b4d0dafcb56529321ac8f111794.jpg","text":"Μπορώ να ανεβώ στην καρέκλα.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10301/size6/817c63927008771778a8aa78fcf1d224.jpg","text":"Αλλά δεν μπορώ να κατέβω κάτω πάλι.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10302/size6/e33f59a901dd498e821d63b844ec7a89.jpg","text":"Μπορώ να ανεβώ στην καρέκλα και μετά στο τραπέζι.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10303/size6/aacafea6d668bb6e461660bd165c889b.jpg","text":"Αλλά δεν μπορώ να κατεβώ κάτω  πάλι.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10304/size6/2f2ce99b6c18ca6bca6369c6d3cfda4b.jpg","text":"\"Μπαμπά, μπαμπά\" φωνάζω.\nΟ πατέρας γελά. \"Σονο΄ύ, μάθε να κατεβαίνεις κάτω\", λέει.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10305/size6/20a9267e0350248a07adf620252839a4.jpg","text":"Φοβάμαι, αλλα δεν κλαίω.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10306/size6/8466d6307263a314c983d7a078f4ead3.jpg","text":"Σιγά σιγά, κατεβαίνω από το τραπέζι, και κατεβαίνω από την καρέκλα.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10307/size6/65f45b5bdfd29af3ff6dcd55c33240b0.jpg","text":"Επιτέλους, έμαθα και εγώ να κατεβαίνω κάτω.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":78}}